@node points 
"Points"

HOW: PICKING POINTS
     1. Use the mouse to click drag or lasso the points you want to use.      
        A. You can pick points by lasso, click or by drag box.
           Hold down the ALT key for drag box else you'll be lassoing.
     
     MANIPULATING points
