        select an action to perform on them (Move, Rotate, Scale...)
     
     2. If you have the drag button on, the only action you can do on
        points is move. You can also lock an axis direction to drag on
        by turning on and of the x,y,z buttons.   


WORKS ON: points - allows picking points and actions on points

