     3. To flip top to bottom in the front view, use Y axis. The Y
        direction is from top to bottom in the front and side
        view. (Get it ?)

WORKS IN: All views

WORKS ON: objects, points ,bones

AFFECTED BY: 1. X,Y and Z buttons
